Sentencas: Effects of infiltrated Pr0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta (PSCo)electrocatalyst on SOFC cathode performance have been studied.
Titulo: Pr0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ electrocatalyst for solid oxide fuel cell cathode introduced via infiltration

Sentencas: Nano-sized particulate catalysts, deposited on surfaces of a composite cathode of Sm2O3 doped CeO2 (SDC) and La1-xSrxCo1-yFeyO3-delta (LSCF), are assumed to effectively widen active sites, or triple phase boundaries, for the oxygen reduction reaction.
Titulo: Pr0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ electrocatalyst for solid oxide fuel cell cathode introduced via infiltration

Sentencas: Area specific resistance of commercially available cells has been decreased by 36-40% with the addition of 23 wt% PSCo electrocatalyst on cathode.
Titulo: Pr0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ electrocatalyst for solid oxide fuel cell cathode introduced via infiltration

Sentencas: Analysis of the impedance spectra demonstrates that PSCo electrocatalyst plays a significant role in dissociation of oxygen molecules and adsorption of oxygen atoms into the cathode.
Titulo: Pr0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ electrocatalyst for solid oxide fuel cell cathode introduced via infiltration

Sentencas: A total of 200 h operation of the cells demonstrated that catalytic activity of PSCo has not been significantly degraded.
Titulo: Pr0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ electrocatalyst for solid oxide fuel cell cathode introduced via infiltration

Sentencas: Simultaneous operations of multiple cells using a parallel-cell testing system have made it possible to compare the performance of several cells with high reliability.
Titulo: Pr0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ electrocatalyst for solid oxide fuel cell cathode introduced via infiltration
